sequenceDiagram
    participant "React Control Panel" as ReactControlPanel
    participant "API/Web Layer" as APIWebLayer
    participant "Application Layer" as ApplicationLayer
    participant "Infrastructure Layer" as InfrastructureLayer

    activate ReactControlPanel
    ReactControlPanel->>ReactControlPanel: 1. 1. Admin clicks 'Create New Report'. UI navigates to wizard, initializes state (Zustand store).
    activate APIWebLayer
    ReactControlPanel->>APIWebLayer: 2. 2. [useEffect] Fetch initial data: GET /api/v1/connectors
    APIWebLayer-->>ReactControlPanel: 200 OK with ConnectorConfiguration[]
    ReactControlPanel->>APIWebLayer: 3. 3. [useEffect] Fetch initial data: GET /api/v1/transformations
    APIWebLayer-->>ReactControlPanel: 200 OK with TransformationScript[]
    ReactControlPanel->>ReactControlPanel: 4. 4. Admin completes multi-step form. UI performs real-time client-side validation and updates state store on input change.
    ReactControlPanel->>APIWebLayer: 5. 5. Admin clicks 'Save'. Submit form: POST /api/v1/reports with ReportConfigurationCreateDTO
    APIWebLayer-->>ReactControlPanel: 201 Created with new report ID, or 400/500 on error
    activate ApplicationLayer
    APIWebLayer->>ApplicationLayer: 6. 6. [Controller Action] Invoke CreateReportAsync(dto)
    ApplicationLayer-->>APIWebLayer: Success(newReportId) or Failure(error)
    ReactControlPanel->>ReactControlPanel: 12. 12. On success, display 'Report Created' notification and redirect to reports list page.

